- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a possibility as the paper uses the Newton polytope of the polynomial, which is a geometric object.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper mentions the underlying valued field consisting of Puiseux series, which is a topic in control theory.
